As for Europeans, it is predictable that the United States will reiterate its demand for increased defence spending from 2% to 5% of GDP. In the absence of an effort in this sense, for the old continent will be much more &nbsp; difficult to have a voice in the chapter in a negotiation that Trump intends to close as soon as possible.

